{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM09_ED2_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x28,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "By her very nature, Ayesha worked hard<CR>on whatever she was doing and became<CR>adept at working for those in the know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No job's too small or hard for Ayesha...<CR>That rumor spread far and wide, and job<CR>requests came from beyond the mountains."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Today, a mountain of job requests are delivered to Ayesha, again..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Umm, as you told me, I went right out to go collect medicine orders, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Maybe I collected a tad too many..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Give me a second. Let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "860 bottles of salve, 360 bottles<CR>of cold remedy, 500 days' worth of<CR>painkillers, 4 barrels of tonic..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Whoa...I've never seen a barrel as a unit to order..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, barrel...<CR>And four barrels at that...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yup. They're barrels. F-o-u-r barrels."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, barrel, barrel, four barrels!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yup. All that, and the delivery due date is one month from now... I think I got a little carried away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "As expected, I guess this doesn't even qualify as just \"a lot.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If necessary, I can negotiate to have the delivery due date extended..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No, it's fine! I recently thought up a good way to do this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "A way to make a lot of medicine, all at once! Using that technique, I think I can manage to do it in a month."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But Sis...aren't you worried that you won't have enough ingredients for all this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "We don't have that many medicinal herbs in storage, do we?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*gasp*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If we gather everything from around here, we'll exhaust the supply and they won't grow back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, what should I do...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Should I shift the deadline then?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No... I can't do it near the workshop, but if I go somewhere else..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If I remember correctly, there was a warren near Hornheim!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ernie, that's it. We'll be fine!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "All right. Then, I'll leave it to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yup. But to do this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I want you to take Nio to Hornheim as soon as possible..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What? But, Nio by herself?<CR>Is that okay...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'll be fine. I've been wandering around all by myself for a long time in some place I don't even understand!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Compared to that, going on some errand is totally easy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then let's go together, Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Thanks for taking me, Ernie!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sis, I'll go accomplish my mission, and I'll look magnificent doing it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay then, Ayesha, we'll be going for a quick run to Hornheim!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Good luck!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, you girls sure are full of energy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "That's our most redeeming feature."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You girls are energizing me, too.<CR>All right, let's do this!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Woohoo!"
        }
    ]
}